snippet.title: McDonald's Indoor Playground Playtime. Happy Meal and Family Fun with Chase and Cole Adventures
snippet.description:
McDonald's Indoor Playground Playtime. Happy Meal and Family Fun with Chase and Cole Adventures. Thank you for watching our Family Channel!

With the rainy weather taking over Memorial Day we had to call an audible. Fortunately, we have a McDonalds playground a few miles down the road from our house, so we took our Holiday Adventure to Ronald's house and his indoor playground. An afternoon of slides, climbs, obstacle courses, and of course, Happy Meals, was just what the doctored ordered. 

The Happy Meal prizes are original board games from my childhood so we have enjoyed the prize surprises just as much as the boys these past few weeks. Connect4 is still my favorite but who doesn't like BattleShip and Operation? Hopefully the weather clears up next weekend so we can take our Adventures to the beach, but we will never complain about an afternoon at McDonalds 😋😛

snippet.title: Busfabriken Indoor Play Family Fun for Kids
snippet.description:
Our summer here in Sweden right now is pretty bad when it comes to the weather. So when it rains, we go inside to play instead. This is Busfabriken lekland in Norrköping, Sweden.

We've been at this indoor playground before, and you might remember these times:

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qplsT8w4ono
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cIwjgaftkuA
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=s9kM-DoEKaQ

This is a super fun indoor play center, and we had a great time as always. 

This indoor play area features these fun attractions:

- Many fun slides
- Tall and very steep drop slide
- Trampolines
- Pedal tricycles
- Tube slides (tunnel slides)
- Volcano slide
- Very tall and large jungle gym
- And much more...

Indoor playground fun for family and kids.
